title: Data Science, the SQL
text:
Welcome to Data Science, the SQL
Daily class notes for Data Science, the SQL, by Jo hardin, SDS 261 at Smith College.
You are responsible for reading your text. Your text is very good & readable, so you should use it. Your text is not, however, overly technical. You should make sure you are coming to class and asking lots of questions.
More information and course details can be found at the SDS261 website.
